                    oc:sectionTitle "Limitations" ],
                [ a oc:Section ;
                    oc:hasSubsection [ a oc:Section ;
                            oc:hasContent [ a oc:CodeExample ;
                                    oc:blockType "code_block" ;
                                    oc:codeContent """## Email Header Deep Dive

### Key Headers to Review
| Header | What It Shows |
|--------|---------------|
| From | Displayed sender |
| Return-Path | Actual reply address |
| Received | Server path (bottom = origin) |
| SPF | Sender authorized? |
| DKIM | Signature valid? |
| DMARC | Policy result |

### Authentication Results
| Result | Meaning |
|--------|---------|
| pass | Legitimate |
| fail | Likely spoofed |
| softfail | Possibly spoofed |
| none | No policy set |
""" ;
